5t-tr%C3%BA-H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n-v%E1%BA%A1n-s%E1%BB%B1-h%C6%B0u/poem-aSGhOUmfSS5Jfj4YjHOqUQ">Nhất trú Hàn Sơn vạn sự hưu - 一住寒山萬事休</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%AD-An-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA/poem-3EtEYotauMJWOh4Awz0OaQ">Tuyệt cú - 絕句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%AD-An-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-Qyf_BWcnPQcxj6qpqNzzzA">Chí An thiền sư</a>)<br></div>	</div>
